Wow!

05:51.101 --> 05:51.977
<i>You protect...</i>

05:54.145 --> 05:55.063
<i>...and prevent...</i>

05:57.440 --> 05:59.025
<i>...and even plan ahead.</i>

06:00.026 --> 06:02.028
<i>But what about your birth control?</i>

06:02.112 --> 06:05.949
<i>Maybe it's time to consider the proven,
permanent birth control of Essure.</i>

06:09.119 --> 06:12.372
Essure is
a permanent sterilization device.

06:13.623 --> 06:16.459
It is made out of
little four-centimeter coils.

06:17.043 --> 06:20.797
It's inserted through the uterus
and placed inside of the fallopian tubes.

06:21.631 --> 06:25.468
It's intentionally designed
to cause an inflammatory response,

06:25.552 --> 06:27.596
which generates scar tissue.

06:28.054 --> 06:31.516
The scar tissue closes off
the fallopian tubes permanently,

06:31.600 --> 06:33.894
blocking the sperm
and the egg from meeting,

06:34.185 --> 06:35.770
therefore preventing pregnancy.

06:37.355 --> 06:40.191
The early studies that were done
to get this device approved

06:40.275 --> 06:42.736
suggested it's 99% effective

06:42.986 --> 06:46.072
in closing the fallopian tube
and causing sterilization.

06:46.489 --> 06:48.658
It originally was designed by Conceptus

06:48.742 --> 06:50.327
and then bought by Bayer.

06:50.410 --> 06:54.164
It was marketed as a better choice
than the traditional tubal ligation

06:54.706 --> 06:57.834
<i>The Essure procedure does not require
any incisions.</i>

06:58.126 --> 07:02.422
<i>And because there are no incisions,
the procedure does not leave any scars.</i>

07:02.714 --> 07:05.884
<i>And when it comes to recovery
after the Essure procedure,</i>

07:06.134 --> 07:08.803
<i>women were typically discharged
from the medical facility</i>

07:08.887 --> 07:11.014
<i>within 45 minutes.</i>

07:11.097 --> 07:14.434
It took no time out of my life.

07:15.101 --> 07:19.648
And there was no chance
of having to go under anesthesia.

07:20.148 --> 07:22.943
I was a nurse assisting
in the placement of Essure

07:23.026 --> 07:24.569
during the clinical trials.

07:25.195 --> 07:28.782
So I watched the procedure.
I thought it was simple.

07:29.115 --> 07:33.578
It was non-surgical, it was permanent,
and it was everything I was looking for.

07:35.330 --> 07:38.792
Seeing how easy it was to put it in,
I thought I should do it too.

07:39.542 --> 07:43.004
<i>For us, we were now allowed
to have a type of intimacy...</i>

07:43.088 --> 07:45.757
The company liked my story
because I was a nurse,

07:45.840 --> 07:48.259
I'd participated
on both ends of the product.

07:48.718 --> 07:51.096
So I was invited to be a spokesperson.

07:51.721 --> 07:55.392
I even went so far as I had my own website
called <i>Ask Gaby.</i>

07:55.892 --> 07:58.687
Patients would to me,
doctors would write to me.

07:58.770 --> 08:00.563
I told them all the benefits.

08:01.272 --> 08:05.443
I used to tell them that it took longer
