09:20.852 --> 09:23.313
<i>Thread the Essure device
through the introducer</i>

09:23.396 --> 09:25.023
<i>while you hold the hysteroscope.</i>

09:25.607 --> 09:28.943
<i>Slowly and steadily advance
the Essure delivery system</i>

09:29.027 --> 09:30.570
<i>into the fallopian tube.</i>

09:31.446 --> 09:33.406
He said I shouldn't feel anything.

09:33.490 --> 09:36.493
Just two little devices
that I wouldn't even notice.

09:37.368 --> 09:40.497
But the moment
