of the clinical trial participants,

01:27:03.885 --> 01:27:09.683
so I had mine implanted in 2000,
and I had mine taken out in 2014.

01:27:10.726 --> 01:27:16.273
I don't know if any of you were familiar
with the <i>Ask Gaby </i> website...

01:27:16.940 --> 01:27:19.943
that was on Conceptus
and Essure's website.

01:27:20.026 --> 01:27:21.111
That was me.

01:27:21.194 --> 01:27:22.571
I was a spokesperson.

01:27:23.780 --> 01:27:27.367
I failed thousands of women
for seven years.

01:27:27.451 --> 01:27:30.245
It's a long time to tell women
that a product is great.

01:27:31.037 --> 01:27:32.998
So the guilt that you live with...

01:27:34.958 --> 01:27:36.376
and the pain...

01:27:38.378 --> 01:27:42.758
and just crazy feelings of responsibility

01:27:42.841 --> 01:27:43.967
because of that.

01:27:48.221 --> 01:27:50.515
Thank you for being
on this side now

01:27:50.599 --> 01:27:54.770
because it's important
that people now see the damage

01:27:54.853 --> 01:27:57.606
and more and more doctors
are starting to see it.

01:27:57.689 --> 01:27:58.690
Very validating.

01:28:03.820 --> 01:28:06.782
We just want to have a discussion
and brainstorm.

01:28:06.865 --> 01:28:09.409
What should our new media push be
right now?

01:28:09.910 --> 01:28:13.663
I felt good about it
'cause I saw women that came together

01:28:13.747 --> 01:28:15.707
to fight for what they believe in.

01:28:16.374 --> 01:28:18.210
They're strong, they're smart women,

01:28:18.293 --> 01:28:20.420
and they're getting the media to listen.

01:28:21.546 --> 01:28:24.466
<i>It was supposed to be safer
and less invasive.</i>

01:28:24.549 --> 01:28:27.886
<i>Why are so many people complaining
about a popular birth control device?</i>

01:28:27.969 --> 01:28:29.304
<i>Pain, back pain.</i>

01:28:29.387 --> 01:28:31.515
<i>It was debilitating. I could barely walk.</i>

01:28:31.598 --> 01:28:34.351
<i>I never thought
I would be looking at a hysterectomy...</i>

01:28:35.101 --> 01:28:35.936
<i>at 29.</i>

01:28:36.019 --> 01:28:37.521
<i>My body is just devastated.</i>

01:28:37.604 --> 01:28:41.441
<i>Damaged, they say,
by a birth control device called Essure.</i>

01:28:41.525 --> 01:28:45.028
The stories started getting out
in the news and then other news stations

01:28:45.111 --> 01:28:49.074
started seeing the other stories and were
like, "Okay, let's do this in our area."

01:28:49.157 --> 01:28:51.743
<i>Five heart-wrenching stories
of extreme physical pain.</i>

01:28:52.327 --> 01:28:54.746
<i>Six women with severe medical problems.</i>

01:28:54.830 --> 01:28:58.875
<i>Thousands of women like Becky
are sharing their experiences on Facebook.</i>

01:28:59.543 --> 01:29:02.254
There are now
35,000 members in the group.

01:29:02.754 --> 01:29:04.881
We've set up groups in other countries.

01:29:04.965 --> 01:29:08.051
We found women in Italy,
willing to take over the page.

01:29:08.134 --> 01:29:09.886
We started the Netherlands group.

01:29:12.848 --> 01:29:14.724
We had women from France.

01:29:16.560 --> 01:29:17.894
They're all branches of us.

01:29:18.937 --> 01:29:22.816
So we've got 11 subgroups
that are other countries.

01:29:23.942 --> 01:29:25.944
<i>A controversial birth control device</i>

01:29:26.027 --> 01:29:28.530
<i>in the US is going off the market
in Europe.</i>

01:29:28.613 --> 01:29:31.575
<i>Bayer announced
it is pulling out of the European market</i>

01:29:31.658 --> 01:29:33.326
<i>due to a lack of interest.</i>

01:29:33.410 --> 01:29:36.580
<i>But a spokesperson says,
"Bayer's decision</i>

01:29:36.663 --> 01:29:41.126
<i>does not impact the sale or marketing
of the product in the United States</i>

01:29:41.209 --> 01:29:43.461
<i>where there continues to be demand,</i>

01:29:43.545 --> 01:29:46.548
<i>despite the recent inaccurate
and biased reporting."</i>

01:29:47.716 --> 01:29:49.009
That's bullshit.

01:29:55.015 --> 01:29:59.269
The equivalent of the FDA in Europe
asked Bayer to provide more safety data.

01:30:00.020 --> 01:30:03.231
And Bayer, at that point, decided
to withdraw it from the market.

01:30:04.316 --> 01:30:05.609
It's very frustrating.

01:30:08.194 --> 01:30:11.156
Our group has been fighting
in our country for the longest.

01:30:12.240 --> 01:30:14.659
Yet we're the ones
with it still on the market.

01:30:17.746 --> 01:30:20.457
Bayer has no incentive
to take it off the market here.

01:30:23.627 --> 01:30:26.046
Nobody's holding the manufacturer
accountable.

01:30:26.671 --> 01:30:29.132
- Bye, honey.
- Bye, honey. Knock 'em dead.

01:30:31.927 --> 01:30:34.387
We're not gonna stop
until it's off the market.

01:30:43.605 --> 01:30:46.983
The FDA isn't doing anything,
the manufacturer's not doing anything.

01:30:47.067 --> 01:30:50.278
We need to push Congress
to force the hand of the FDA.

01:30:51.613 --> 01:30:55.700
So this device
is still being inserted in women?

01:30:55.784 --> 01:30:57.953
- In the United States...
- In the US?

01:30:58.036 --> 01:31:01.498
September 18th, it came
off the market everywhere else.

01:31:01.581 --> 01:31:04.709
Look at how far up
the injury and death reports go now.

01:31:04.793 --> 01:31:06.836
Because they're not being held liable,

01:31:06.920 --> 01:31:10.298
they don't have any incentive
to take these devices off the market.

01:31:10.382 --> 01:31:14.344
People are getting harmed and injured,
and nobody's doing anything about it.

01:31:15.512 --> 01:31:18.723
We have many, many women
who are ending up with fragments

01:31:18.807 --> 01:31:21.434
and massive issues and re-surgeries.

01:31:21.518 --> 01:31:24.145
- Women just seem to be expendable.
- Yes.

01:31:24.229 --> 01:31:27.440
That's how we're starting to feel.
We're disposable.

01:31:27.524 --> 01:31:30.986
The FDA has been very clear that they're
not going to take this off the market.

01:31:31.069 --> 01:31:33.905
That this is the manufacturer's
responsibility

01:31:33.989 --> 01:31:35.865
I know of no possible reason,

01:31:35.949 --> 01:31:40.829
when they are chosen to protect
the health of the people of this country,

01:31:40.912 --> 01:31:43.123
that they would choose to go
in the other direction

01:31:43.206 --> 01:31:45.041
and protect the manufacturers.

01:31:45.125 --> 01:31:46.668
That's gotta be changed.

01:31:48.211 --> 01:31:53.925
I wanted to get as much information as
