01:31:54.426 --> 01:31:57.429
I don't know
how many of those that you have.

01:31:58.054 --> 01:31:58.888
A lot.

01:31:58.972 --> 01:32:00.640
- Thousands.
- Tens of thousands.

01:32:00.724 --> 01:32:01.975
Tens of thousands, okay.

